ClientBrowser.name: ClientBrowser
ClientBrowser.description: Represents a cookie added to the browser upon login, and also includes information about the browser application where the cookie was inserted.

FullUserAgent.description: Detailed information about the client (browser). For example, Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.0.1) Gecko/2008070208 Firefox/3.0.1

LastUpdate.description: Represents the last time the cookie was changed.

UsersId.description: The ID of the user associated with this item.
